321    /**
322     * Parse --INI-- section key value pairs and return as array.
323     */
324    private function parseIniSection(array|string $content, array $ini = []): array
325    {
326        if (is_string($content)) {
327            $content = explode("\n", trim($content));
328        }
329
330        foreach ($content as $setting) {
331            if (!str_contains($setting, '=')) {
332                continue;
333            }
334
335            $setting = explode('=', $setting, 2);
336            $name    = trim($setting[0]);
337            $value   = trim($setting[1]);
338
339            if ($name === 'extension' || $name === 'zend_extension') {
340                if (!isset($ini[$name])) {
341                    $ini[$name] = [];
342                }
343
344                $ini[$name][] = $value;
345
346                continue;
347            }
348
349            $ini[$name] = $value;
350        }
351
352        return $ini;
353    }
354
355    private function parseEnvSection(string $content): array
356    {
357        $env = [];
358
359        foreach (explode("\n", trim($content)) as $e) {
360            $e = explode('=', trim($e), 2);
361
362            if ($e[0] !== '' && isset($e[1])) {
363                $env[$e[0]] = $e[1];
364            }
365        }
366
367        return $env;
368    }

370    /**
371     * @throws Exception
372     * @throws ExpectationFailedException
373     */
374    private function assertPhptExpectation(array $sections, string $output): void
375    {
376        $assertions = [
377            'EXPECT'      => 'assertEquals',
378            'EXPECTF'     => 'assertStringMatchesFormat',
379            'EXPECTREGEX' => 'assertMatchesRegularExpression',
380        ];
381
382        $actual = preg_replace('/\r\n/', "\n", trim($output));
383
384        foreach ($assertions as $sectionName => $sectionAssertion) {
385            if (isset($sections[$sectionName])) {
386                $sectionContent = preg_replace('/\r\n/', "\n", trim($sections[$sectionName]));
387                $expected       = $sectionName === 'EXPECTREGEX' ? "/{$sectionContent}/" : $sectionContent;
388
389                Assert::$sectionAssertion($expected, $actual);
390
391                return;
392            }
393        }
394
395        throw new InvalidPhptFileException;
396    }

398    private function shouldTestBeSkipped(array $sections, array $settings): bool
399    {
400        if (!isset($sections['SKIPIF'])) {
401            return false;
402        }
403
404        $skipif    = $this->render($sections['SKIPIF']);
405        $jobResult = $this->phpUtil->runJob($skipif, $this->stringifyIni($settings));
406
407        if (!strncasecmp('skip', ltrim($jobResult['stdout']), 4)) {
408            $message = '';
409
410            if (preg_match('/^\s*skip\s*(.+)\s*/i', $jobResult['stdout'], $skipMatch)) {
411                $message = substr($skipMatch[1], 2);
412            }
413
414            EventFacade::emitter()->testSkipped(
415                $this->valueObjectForEvents(),
416                $message,
417            );
418
419            EventFacade::emitter()->testFinished($this->valueObjectForEvents(), 0);
420
421            return true;
422        }
423
424        return false;
425    }

427    private function runClean(array $sections, bool $collectCoverage): void
428    {

431

434
435            $this->phpUtil->runJob($cleanCode, $this->settings($collectCoverage));
436        }
437    }

439    /**
440     * @throws Exception
441     */
442    private function parse(): array
443    {
444        $sections = [];
445        $section  = '';
446
447        $unsupportedSections = [
448            'CGI',
449            'COOKIE',
450            'DEFLATE_POST',
451            'EXPECTHEADERS',
452            'EXTENSIONS',
453            'GET',
454            'GZIP_POST',
455            'HEADERS',
456            'PHPDBG',
457            'POST',
458            'POST_RAW',
459            'PUT',
460            'REDIRECTTEST',
461            'REQUEST',
462        ];
463
464        $lineNr = 0;
465
466        foreach (file($this->filename) as $line) {
467            $lineNr++;
468
469            if (preg_match('/^--([_A-Z]+)--/', $line, $result)) {
470                $section                        = $result[1];
471                $sections[$section]             = '';
472                $sections[$section . '_offset'] = $lineNr;
473
474                continue;
475            }
476
477            if (empty($section)) {
478                throw new InvalidPhptFileException;
479            }
480
481            $sections[$section] .= $line;
482        }
483
484        if (isset($sections['FILEEOF'])) {
485            $sections['FILE'] = rtrim($sections['FILEEOF'], "\r\n");
486            unset($sections['FILEEOF']);
487        }
488
489        $this->parseExternal($sections);
490
491        if (!$this->validate($sections)) {
492            throw new InvalidPhptFileException;
493        }
494
495        foreach ($unsupportedSections as $section) {
496            if (isset($sections[$section])) {
497                throw new UnsupportedPhptSectionException($section);
498            }
499        }
500
501        return $sections;
502    }

504    /**
505     * @throws Exception
506     */

695    private function getLocationHintFromDiff(string $message, array $sections): array
696    {
697        $needle       = '';
698        $previousLine = '';
699        $block        = 'message';
700
701        foreach (preg_split('/\r\n|\r|\n/', $message) as $line) {
702            $line = trim($line);
703
704            if ($block === 'message' && $line === '--- Expected') {
705                $block = 'expected';
706            }
707
708            if ($block === 'expected' && $line === '@@ @@') {
709                $block = 'diff';
710            }
711
712            if ($block === 'diff') {
713                if (str_starts_with($line, '+')) {
714                    $needle = $this->getCleanDiffLine($previousLine);
715
716                    break;
717                }
718
719                if (str_starts_with($line, '-')) {
720                    $needle = $this->getCleanDiffLine($line);
721
722                    break;
723                }
724            }
725
726            if (!empty($line)) {
727                $previousLine = $line;
728            }
729        }
730
731        return $this->getLocationHint($needle, $sections);
732    }

737            $line = $matches[2];
738        }
739
740        return $line;

743    private function getLocationHint(string $needle, array $sections): array
744    {
745        $needle = trim($needle);
746
747        if (empty($needle)) {
748            return [[
749                'file' => realpath($this->filename),
750                'line' => 1,
751            ]];
752        }
753
754        $search = [
755            // 'FILE',
756            'EXPECT',
757            'EXPECTF',
758            'EXPECTREGEX',
759        ];
760
761        foreach ($search as $section) {
762            if (!isset($sections[$section])) {
763                continue;
764            }
765
766            if (isset($sections[$section . '_EXTERNAL'])) {
767                $externalFile = trim($sections[$section . '_EXTERNAL']);
768
769                return [
770                    [
771                        'file' => realpath(dirname($this->filename) . DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR . $externalFile),
772                        'line' => 1,
773                    ],
774                    [
775                        'file' => realpath($this->filename),
776                        'line' => ($sections[$section . '_EXTERNAL_offset'] ?? 0) + 1,
777                    ],
778                ];
779            }
780
781            $sectionOffset = $sections[$section . '_offset'] ?? 0;
782            $offset        = $sectionOffset + 1;
783
784            foreach (preg_split('/\r\n|\r|\n/', $sections[$section]) as $line) {
785                if (str_contains($line, $needle)) {
786                    return [
787                        [
788                            'file' => realpath($this->filename),
789                            'line' => $offset,
790                        ],
791                    ];
792                }
793
794                $offset++;
795            }
796        }
797
798        return [
799            [
800                'file' => realpath($this->filename),
801                'line' => 1,
802            ],
803        ];
804    }
